{
  "stem": "26983.8",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This one SS she killed, Schellinger or so was his name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course they killed her afterward.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They killed many people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She killed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was dancing a different, and somehow around, and-- that he told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then he told me many stories about how people behaved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometimes transfer of Jews from ghettos, and how the mentality of people is that everyone wants to live another minute, and is willing to sacrifice just to live another minute.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So sometimes there came very strong men, and the Sonderkommando tried to encourage them that they should make some resistance.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the minute the Germans saw it, they choose one, the women or some of the elderly, and told them if you will calm them and so on, we will let you live or something like that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But of course they never have done it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So all kinds of not so pleasant stories he told me of how people behaved.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If they didn't let them easily in, there was a special place with only sticks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was the second time I saw these famous sticks, a little chamber with only sticks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I asked him, what is this, when I was led in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, well, that's for the stick commander.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they don't want to go we have to--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there I also saw--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they could kill as far as they told me, a whole transport overnight, 2,500 people in one crematorium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It depends if he had to wait in the queue--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very smooth?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean he was in the gas chamber, he was around 20 minutes--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--half an hour, as far as they told me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then only they took the corpse out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later I saw the places, exactly.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
